xwikidoc.title: Hill Giant Priestess
xwikidoc.content:
[[image:HillGiantPriestess.png||style="float: right;"]]Female Hill Giants often practice a form of shamanistic magic. They can be quite deadly. Adventurers invading the hill giants lairs may quickly discover that the brutish male hill giants are the least of their problems.
== Tactics ==
Hill Giant Priestesses will usually stand back and use their Earth Lash and Earth Wave powers to slow down and confuse the enemy as their brutish husbands wade into battle. If necessary they will use their clubs to defend themselves and can do so quite competently. In defense of their dwellings and children they will fight to the death.
